 - Known issues -

* Playback of playlist videos fails 
    Another problem that seems to occur with builds using DVDPlayer. It works
    fine on xbox builds with mplayer
    
    
    
    
 - General information -

This plugin is written for The mediacenter, also known as XBMC and
can be found at www.xbmc.org
It's main purpose is to scrape media content from www.nrk.no and feed it to
XBMC as virtual folders. 




 - Installation -
 
For installation of this plugin refer to:
http://xbmc.org/wiki/?title=HOW-TO_install_and_use_plugins_in_XBMC





